reviewText:
If you're familiar w/ the products of Peach, Vivid's soft-core division, you'll know what you're getting w/ this one. In a nutshell, some decent babes, a couple real hotties, and some sexy skin in dance vignettes & that type stuff. Nothing awesome, but nice.

This one's good - not enough pink (never is), but hot fun. One vignette features a busty, double D babe washing a car that is worth the price by itself.

Nice item, pick it up cheap, enjoy & sell it back on amazon.
